data.description: Immaculately maintained ranch home in quiet Sunset Ridge. Peace and serenity abound at this charming cul-de-sac oasis. The current owner has spent countless hours caring for and curating this home. Sited on an 8,456 sf lot, you will find 50-60 rose bushes throughout the property, 20 peony bushes, a lovely apple tree, a gazebo which is covered in a thriving clematis! The yard is fully enclosed and includes a detached storage structure built by the owner! Interior features include an open floor plan, newer laminate flooring throughout, three bedrooms and one full bath, a large eat-in kitchen, an attached single car garage plus ample street parking. The roof was replaced in 2017, the furnace and hot water heater and most appliances have been replaced within the past 5-10 years, and the windows were all replaced during the time this owner has been here! The HOA is minimal and is more of a road association. Located just steps to Downtown LaPorte, Watson Lake and the Poudre River!
